Dear Peter,

Looking the figure I think not average of x, rather its maximum change 
with the distance from the equator.
You could try the quantile regression (quantreg package) developed to 
such cases. An introduction to this method for ecologists can be 
downloaded from here:
http://www.econ.uiuc.edu/~roger/research/rq/QReco.pdf

Best wishes

Zoltan



